description: Returns an array of  XssMatchSet objects.

nested_items.name: NextMarker
nested_items.description: If you have more  XssMatchSet objects than the number that you specified for Limit in the request, the response includes a NextMarker value. To list more XssMatchSet objects, submit another ListXssMatchSets request, and specify the NextMarker value from the response in the NextMarker value in the next request.

nested_items.name: XssMatchSetId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for an XssMatchSet. You use XssMatchSetId to get information about a XssMatchSet (see  GetXssMatchSet), update an XssMatchSet (see  UpdateXssMatchSet), insert an XssMatchSet into a Rule or delete one from a Rule (see  UpdateRule), and delete an XssMatchSet from AWS WAF (see  DeleteXssMatchSet).

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: The name of the XssMatchSet, if any, specified by Id.
